<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/700114-do-anyone-in-this-book-actually-consider">Do anyone in this book actually consider to commit suicide since it listed in &quot;Suicide&quot;?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_700114'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F72159.Cat_on_a_Hot_Tin_Roof">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/700114-do-anyone-in-this-book-actually-consider">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/700114-do-anyone-in-this-book-actually-consider">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/23143346-kankan"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1484723113i/23143346._UX100_CR0,12,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/23143346-kankan">Kankan</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Yes. It is known that a character commits suicide but the play takes place in the aftermath of that suicide. 
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

