        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2428199395" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3189289224407731782">I&apos;m not sure that you can consider yourself a &quot;southerner&quot; or even from the south if you have not read Tennessee Williams&apos; plays - all of them. I may be a transplanted Hoosier now, but rest assured, I have read and adore all of Williams&apos; plays. They are, without a doubt, some of the very best of American literature and, by far, in the top tier of Southern Lit. This, Cat on a Hot Tin Roof, is one of his best! </span>
  <span id="freeText3189289224407731782" style="display:none">I'm not sure that you can consider yourself a "southerner" or even from the south if you have not read Tennessee Williams' plays - all of them. I may be a transplanted Hoosier now, but rest assured, I have read and adore all of Williams' plays. They are, without a doubt, some of the very best of American literature and, by far, in the top tier of Southern Lit. This, Cat on a Hot Tin Roof, is one of his best! </span>
