<li class='cover' id='bookCover_14940'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/14940.Who_s_Afraid_of_Virginia_Woolf_"><img alt="Who&#39;s Afraid of Virginia Woolf?" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1327962277l/14940._SX98_.jpg" />
